-- MOVES-Lombard Odier appoints Andrea Argenti head of Italy business
-- By Anya George Tharakan in Bangalore
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 12:18PM EDT
-- None



Sept 26 (Reuters) - Geneva-based Lombard Odier Investment Managers (LOIM) appointed Andrea Argenti country head for Italy, effective December.

Argenti previously worked at BlackRock Investment Management for 14 years and spent about eight years as head of the firm's retail business in Italy.